# But although I try to make myself

77
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,700
# As pleasant as I can

78
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,800
# Yet everybody says
I am a disagreeable man

79
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,800
# And I can't think why

80
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,700
# He can't think why

81
