00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:10,600
# Noisome hags of night

680
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:13,800
# Imps of deadly shade

681
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:15,600
# Pallid ghosts

682
00:45:15,800 --> 00:45:17,300
# Arise in hosts

683
00:45:17,500 --> 00:45:20,300
# And lend me all your aid

684
00:45:20,600 --> 00:45:22,100
# Appear!

685
00:45:22,400 --> 00:45:24,100
# Appear!

686
00:45:24,300 --> 00:45:27,300
# Appear!

687
00:45:32,300 --> 00:45:36,900
# Good master, we are here!

688
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:40,100
# Hark, hark, they assemble

689
00:45:40,400 --> 00:45:42,200
# These fiends of the night

690
00:45:42,500 --> 00:45:44,400
# Oh, Alexis, I tremble

691
00:45:44,600 --> 00:45:46,700
# Seek safety in flight!

692
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:49,000
# Let us fly to a far-off land

693
